Glaze is a content driven discussion platform where the discussion is annotated (glazed) on the content.

Dependencies:

# Python 2.6 +
# MySQLdb
# sudo easy_install webpy
# cd ./glaze/data
# mysql -u root < schema.sql


Run
# cd {~/code/glaze/glaze}$ python handlers.py
# open http://0.0.0.0:8080/2004-06-30-World-Class-Supply-Management